{"title":"fix(remediation): set REQUIRED_API_BASE env in vigil-app Deployment","body":"Root cause: REQUIRED_API_BASE environment variable was set to an empty string in the Deployment manifest, causing nginx to fail with "invalid number of arguments in proxy_pass directive" during startup.

Evidence: 2026/06/07 15:22:47 [emerg] 1#1: invalid number of arguments in "proxy_pass" directive in /etc/nginx/conf.d/default.conf:4

Fix: Set REQUIRED_API_BASE to 'http://api-backend:8080' in the vigil-app Deployment."}

